parameters: Hey, do you think you could do me
and my partner here a favor?
We were just mindin' our own business here when that stupid
slot machine decided to help itself to a bit too much change.
He gambled all of our money away.
That's only because the machines are rigged!
You'll get us kicked out for talk like that.
Who cares? Anyway, me and my partner Polar here,
I'm Solar by the way, me and my partner are mercenaries,
and we're good at what we do.
So, you wouldn't happen to have a job for us, would ya?
You don't? Well, great. This is just great.
Crud, I feel like a real jerk right now.
